shorttext: Irisa Stars Oil is a blended oil with a 4:3 ratio of THC to CBD, very mild THC potency and no taste.
title: Stars Oil (4 mg/ml THC, 3 mg/ml CBD)
description: Irisa Stars Oil is a blended formulation with a 4:3 ratio of THC to CBD, and it’s made with the ethanol extraction method. The terpenes have been removed from this oil, which has very mild THC potency. It comes in 30 ml bottles, and the indoor-grown strain is also available as a massage oil and in pre-rolled packs of three. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.
